STATE of North Carolina
v.
Justin Michael TYSON No. 253P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 27, 2019 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of North Carolina. Justin Michael Tyson, For Tyson, Justin Michael. Kimberly S. Robb, District Attorney.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 27th of June 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Pitt County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 27th of June 2019."
